00001 ******************************************************************09/12/90
00002 * THIS PROCEDURE DIVISION COPY BOOK IS USED TO GET AND FORMAT    *DPPD018 
00003 * THE CURRENT TIME ONLY, FOR PROGRAMS UNDER THE NEW CICS         *   LV001
00004 * ARCHITECTURE.                                                  *DPPD018 
00005 * COPY MEMBER DPWS017 CONTAINS ALL VARIABLES REQUIRED FOR THIS   *DPPD018 
00006 * ROUTINE.                                                       *DPPD018 
00007 ******************************************************************DPPD018 
00008  SKIP1                                                            DPPD018 
00009  DP018-0000-GET-CURR-TIME.                                        DPPD018 
00010  SKIP2                                                            DPPD018 
00011      EXEC CICS                                                    DPPD018 
00012          ASKTIME                                                  DPPD018 
00013              ABSTIME (DP017-CURRENT-ABSTIME)                      DPPD018 
00014      END-EXEC.                                                    DPPD018 
00015  SKIP1                                                            DPPD018 
00016      EXEC CICS                                                    DPPD018 
00017          FORMATTIME                                               DPPD018 
00018              ABSTIME (DP017-CURRENT-ABSTIME)                      DPPD018 
00019              TIME    (DP017-EDITED-TIME-HMS)                      DPPD018 
00020              TIMESEP (':')                                        DPPD018 
00021      END-EXEC.                                                    DPPD018 
00022  SKIP1                                                            DPPD018 
00023      MOVE DP017-EDITED-TIME-HMS  TO ATIMEO.                       DPPD018 
00024 *DP018-0000-EXIT.                                                 DPPD018 
